{"tid":889251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港隊東亞杯決選名單已公佈","createTime":"2018-11-04T12:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T12:59:43.000Z","uid":62073,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c1698011e738c18d62a2a3dd3892e5fe20c4e2c3","tid":889251,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"【征戰 EAFF E-1！香港隊決選名單！】<br />\n<br />\n香港隊決選名單出爐喇！嚟緊香港隊將會出戰東亞足球錦標賽外圍賽第二圈，20人大軍名單將會喺5/11開始球隊訓練，9/11就會出發喇！<br />\n<br />\n今次香港隊去台灣，將會6日踢3場比賽，對手分別係中華台北、朝鮮及蒙古。香港隊要加油啊，球迷們，一齊撐港隊力爭出線決賽週啦！<br />\n<br />\n備註：陳嘉豪（佳聯元朗）、黃梓浩（東方龍獅）及 鍾偉強（和富大埔）被挑選作替補球員，將於 5/11-8/11 跟隨港隊訓練，如決選名單中的球員受傷，將會由他們替補。<br />\n<br />\n#香港勁揪 #撐自己人 #東亞足球錦標賽外圍賽第二圈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/04/200648_b3cb367a2707dad689cd9efbf8afaa01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F04%2F200648_b3cb367a2707dad689cd9efbf8afaa01.jpg&h=c2561812&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30dcbd9f453343f71ba0d7c28d7d94e365754474","tid":889251,"uid":9030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個應入但入唔到"},{"pid":"5c7aee2424d48aa4cd2feb581740e61859db65be","tid":889251,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"Tsun今次又咩原因"},{"pid":"115ddb2beb31c457b9159b3237665d9bcab30562","tid":889251,"uid":62073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30dcbd9f453343f71ba0d7c28d7d94e365754474","tid":889251,"uid":9030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"有冇邊個應入但入唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:10:54.000Z","msg":"閘位唔掂<br />\n無肥jack可惜"},{"pid":"dd68a5e9e42b9c8db7851f7a7b0d3ab78e4d48d5","tid":889251,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"Dani一星期踢3場90分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b22cf83f32458a1d34361ddc8fca8bb694c4be4","tid":889251,"uid":37528,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"5c7aee2424d48aa4cd2feb581740e61859db65be","tid":889251,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"Tsun今次又咩原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"廢"},{"pid":"b7929d8d79a9e4fae41454cf7e4d5986beb176d2","tid":889251,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"中村係咪真係無得踢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78af6840275d8af4964957e5c8a0f128d6a07cde","tid":889251,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"徐宏傑傷？"},{"pid":"b34cc44dc5a80cd081b12a75fbd3eacdd6265ba6","tid":889251,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"戴狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef632ba93f5e4bd0739ae8138e09dcdd8cfdad8b","tid":889251,"uid":62073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7929d8d79a9e4fae41454cf7e4d5986beb176d2","tid":889251,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"中村係咪真係無得踢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"初選一早交左名單唔可以改，所以中村果d等下次"},{"pid":"9b971e36fa3a262214bc5815cade4c41eb032891","tid":889251,"uid":70040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b34cc44dc5a80cd081b12a75fbd3eacdd6265ba6","tid":889251,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"戴狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"去咗踢中国隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0688303d8275af00b65dd59772478d6a75f68e4","tid":889251,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"展龍沒?"},{"pid":"d86cc213bc975e084b2cb0ca27ed4579f9e72fbd","tid":889251,"uid":62073,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"韋特又被問到戴偉浚落選的原因及有否再與對方聯絡，但只以「戴偉浚並不在名單之中」作簡單回答。至於效力梅州客家的徐宏傑則因為在昨日的聯賽中受傷而落選，韋特指不論對「傑仔」還是球隊都非常可惜。另外，法圖斯效力的貴州恆豐已提早降班，韋特指希望球會能提早放人並讓法圖斯在星期二加入訓練：「對他們已無事可爭，但對我們來說就還有很多東西要去爭取。」翻查中超賽程，貴州恆豐將在星期三晚作客河南建業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於球隊在台灣的目標，韋特坦言要創造歷史：「我們面對朝鮮從未贏過，當然希望創造歷史，而且最重要是晉級決賽週。」港隊明日將在將軍澳足總足球訓練中心開操，4日後中午啟程前往台北。東亞錦第二圈預賽的3場賽程分別是11日對中華台北、13日對朝鮮及16日對蒙古。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/226747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F226747&d=1ZBYsp%2FwIU%2BXG7hVFOcWV%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9e2c8a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/226747</a>"},{"pid":"bad7279c5b85decbdfb52b6007d33c2425b8c3a6","tid":889251,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b971e36fa3a262214bc5815cade4c41eb032891","tid":889251,"uid":70040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b34cc44dc5a80cd081b12a75fbd3eacdd6265ba6","tid":889251,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"戴狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"去咗踢中国隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e012b2ed0120fb34e397f4388d4561a999fb20e3"